Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  老公
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…牙齒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.52,0:01:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,植根於先祖血肉內的植物之苗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸展開茂盛繁盛的枝葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而結出豐碩累累的果實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:01:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能賣我點吃的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看這田地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為夏天出奇的冷天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結出的糧食已經非常少了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別抱指望啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去山那頭的村子看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年只有那裡豐收了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.35,0:02:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別出鬼點子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡的米沒有問題才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,災年還能豐收
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是先祖的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒的豐收…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒的豐收…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有誰要被先祖帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年會是誰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先祖會優先選擇身體虛弱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…這田真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？有事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:03:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我只是想問問有沒有多餘的糧食能賣給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可沒有多餘的糧食
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是每年都能收穫足夠的糧食
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要儲糧時還是得儲糧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今年的豐收算是奇蹟…囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直有好好地祭祀祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九泉下的祖先也一直保護著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代價是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須有個人被帶走…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不是先祖該做的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是…沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒試過怎麼知道沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能跟我說說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個村子的田地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大災年的時候豐收
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是很早以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而當年秋天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會有人的嘴裡長出「瑞齒」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種牙齒會在秋天結束時掉落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人也會…隨之死去…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那人的生命也認為是從先祖那裡獲得豐收的祭品…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種說法一直這樣流傳著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  大家還是感謝先祖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有這個奇蹟的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也許沒辦法在這片貧瘠的土地上一直生存
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被選中的人有什麼共同點嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說都是從身體虛弱的人開始選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體是土葬嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉落的牙齒呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.72,0:04:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「瑞齒」都被祭師師父供奉在祭堂裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭師？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責村裡一切祭奠活動的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我會繼承祭師的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而被教導各種祭祀事務
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「瑞齒」脫落不久  就只有祭師師父能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  必須由祭師師父來舉行祭奠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼要繼承祭師的位置呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我和祭師師父一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時常…能看到常人看不見的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想見你說的那個祭師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭師師父
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在田裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,農耕的書
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有日記
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人真是少見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是蟲師銀古
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找尋「破落的果實」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙樂  你現在應該在田裡幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:11.90,jinggao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}(注：這裡音譯的人名「サネ」即為「実」，日文意義中的「果實」)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹完再回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年是豐收
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好準備可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  還在擔心你媽的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  把這個拿去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說很久以前也有蟲師來過我們這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只是白跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡根本沒有那種果實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你也相信豐收是先祖顯靈嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先祖顯靈嗎？當然有這原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家因為強烈的信仰才能在這塊土地上生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長久以來我們也在一直研究使土地肥沃的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此有時也會有這樣的大豐收
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年的糧食產量也在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  「瑞齒」你怎麼看？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人成年後還會有可能繼續長牙齒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且和種地沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你還是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能問問嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該知道「破落的果實」的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我從長輩那裡聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個蟲師封印在「光脈」裡的東西…據說是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該也能感覺到「光脈」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像有能看見「蟲」的體質
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「蟲」就是這種發光的微小東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「蟲」的根源與「光酒」相近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂「光脈」就是「光酒」流淌的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以說是「生命」的本質
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運用得當的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永生或復活什麼的都能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是蟲師最大的禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也會有例外出現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種果實就是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋在土裡的話就能使周圍獲得一年的豐收
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為代價一個生命體將會被帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這便是我們蟲師之中流傳的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你找到那果實的話你打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消滅它？還是利用它？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我也想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你的話你會怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道犧牲一人便能拯救更多人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而獲得這種果實的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會利用它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有這種果實的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼見很多人餓死就是罪過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知有一人會死還是種下果實的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就等同於殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被拯救的人再多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去的人也只是作為祭品而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是這樣的罪過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人還是會做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去一個人的性命就能拯救兩個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一年這麼短時間的話確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用過一次後就會想用第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那果實是會成長的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨使用次數增加它的影響力也會增加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會把一切的平衡破壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就是說不要用嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣閒置而不用嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也沒在這裡生活過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在事態惡化前還是離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片土地裡還埋葬著先祖的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖祖輩輩的辛勤的汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滲透在每一片土地裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對我們而言是唯一的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道種下了異形的物種的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不算是對這片土地的玷汙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也只是萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的出現那種果實的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會…慎重考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的果實只會使一個人無法存活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而收穫的稻穗則會垂下重重的頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註定會從耕者的掌心滑出  灑落在這土地上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之後  人類的悲歡離合  它們永遠感覺不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你們談完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你會幫我們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不過需要得到全村人的同意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先我得先把「詛咒的豐收」有關的一切內情告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能把大家集合起來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  到底為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想勸大伙燒掉田地嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在再次有人長「瑞齒」之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把果實消滅的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終於承認了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的想法是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒了田地的話誰都活不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把大家都餓死嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要搬離這裡一年就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一時分散到其它土地上生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一年的話應該能行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了春天燒剩的灰燼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該能使土地肥沃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開這裡後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道會有幾人會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家因為不知道內情才會忍耐至今
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都以為真的是先祖顯靈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不允許誰對大伙胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭師師父
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你師父得了什麼病嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是最近他總是身體不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時不時就要喝藥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:12:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這個罐子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不知道你為何會喝這種毒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你想就這樣死掉來逃避責任嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲師先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說要燒田時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得出你的目的不是那種果實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我成為那種果實的最後的犧牲者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說把「破落的果實」帶到村子裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上上任的祭師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:14:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以後  每逢災害的時候就使用這種果實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為避免不必要的混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種果實的存在只有代代的祭師才能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從我做了祭師後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決意不再使用這種果實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到二十年前那場天災
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還得用那果實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我只是想村裡的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就…沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有注意到妻子瞞著我身體不適的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長了「瑞齒」的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  我有個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要吃田裡的糧食
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你也死去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要吃一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的命能讓你存活的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算死也不害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我咀嚼著這樣的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體只是貪婪的吸收著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子脫落的「瑞齒」變成的果實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算扔掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又想到總有一天又會有天災降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次使用時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再看到誰犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而今年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於天災又降臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來我體內結出的果實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算交給沙樂處理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種果實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果埋入你所說的「光脈流」的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會融入裡面而消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是說不清楚那到底是種什麼果實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該比任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都想在這裡活下去  看到村子的將來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看得見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不懈努力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土地會慢慢肥沃起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天人們不靠這種果實也定能生存
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道這將是多少代之後的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我估計是看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就如你所願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你再回答我一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭師師父
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽應該沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了飯後人也精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說不會有事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  沙樂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  沙樂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼今年的祝詞和往年不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  現在還沒有人長「瑞齒」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  還沒有聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的豐收不是「詛咒的豐收」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…難道是我們努力的成果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭奠很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有意外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會照您的囑咐做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭師師父
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在起我做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要和任何人說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說光酒是生命的本質
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是並不代表直接飲用就能讓人復活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能使之成為現實的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種果實應該行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是我猜測
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果吃掉那果實的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動物復活的事應該也能辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和植物一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕光脈會成為你身體的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變成不死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越生物的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你能接受嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你們最大的禁忌嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做這種事難道會被允許嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不說的話不會被發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會成功與否我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道這樣後你能否幸福的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  只是賭博
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許只是加重你的傷  而確定這種果實的存在而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣玷污我的手也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好考慮考慮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不必考慮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…果然還是想看著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片土地的將來會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是憑自己的努力會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在村裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片土地上的人們為這次豐收雀躍不已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.18,0:22:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.26,0:22:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一則奇妙的傳說流傳開來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.50,0:22:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長久的「詛咒的豐收」沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當年結出的糧食
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.34,0:22:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使一個男人起死回生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.62,0:22:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來那個男人不老不死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.29,0:22:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊遍各國
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾回來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片土地就會再現生機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說他是回去傳授新的耕作方法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}棲硯之白


